text: @jcstua Joseph - Hello, this is Teresa and I am very sorry to hear this has happened. Safety is extremely important to FedEx. We will not tolerate any irresponsible acts. I would like to escalate this to the proper department, but will need additional information. Would you please....

@jcstua DM the time this occurred, along with the date. If you would, please provide the city or nearest city where this occurred along with the highway/road name.  I would also appreciate any other details you can remember. Please also provide your name and  phone number for follow-up.
